    {
      "instruction": "<p>After the initial 20 min, remove the tray[s] from the oven and push the potatoes to one side</p><p>Add your <strong>smoked streaky bacon </strong>to the other side of the tray[s], then return it to the oven and cook for a further 12-15 min or until the bacon is golden and crispy</p>",
