    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>mayo </strong>and<strong> grated garlic </strong>(not a big garlic fan? Try using less!) in a small bowl with your <strong>white wine vinegar</strong>, the<strong> remaining dried oregano </strong>and 1/2 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3/4 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[1 tsp]<strong> </span>sugar</strong></p><p>Add a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and<strong> pepper </strong>and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>garlic ranch dressing</strong></p>",
