    {
      "instruction": "<p>To serve, layer the <strong>shredded lettuce</strong>, <strong>sliced egg</strong>, <strong>chopped tomato</strong>, <strong>streaky</strong> <strong>bacon</strong>, <strong>sliced avocado </strong>and<strong> smoky potatoes </strong>in rows – this is your <strong>bacon cobb salad</strong></p><p>Drizzle the<strong> garlic ranch dressing </strong>over everything</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
